INPUT: clinical text (query or document)
│
│
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  PIPELINE 1: CUI REDUCTION                                         ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
│
├── STAGE 1: EXTRACTION + CONTEXT
│   │
│   ├── UMLS extraction API (vector similarity over 2.3M concepts)
│   │   TOP_K=6, TOP_P=5000, COMBINED=True
│   │   retry: 3/1s on 429,5xx | token refresh on 401
│   │
│   ├── ConText negation/temporal detection (medspacy, 102 built-in rules)
│   │   batch_parse: tokenize once, all phrases as spans, run once
│   │   output: negated / historical / hypothetical / family per phrase
│   │   negated → discard all CUIs for that phrase
│   │
│   ├── caching: API distances cached, ConText NEVER cached
│   │
│   └── output: raw CUIs per phrase
│
├── STAGE 2: SAB FILTER
│   │
│   ├── ALLOWED_SABS = {"SNOMEDCT_US"}
│   │   one vocabulary = one consistent hierarchy
│   │   extend with RXNORM (meds), LNC (labs) per use case
│   │
│   └── output: SNOMED-only CUIs
│
├── STAGE 3: METADATA + IC
│   │
│   ├── BigQuery fetch: semantic types, preferred terms
│   │   _BQ_BATCH=5000, _BQ_TIMEOUT=300s
│   │
│   ├── IC = −log((descendants + 1) / total_nodes)
│   │   precomputed for 2.3M nodes, runtime = O(1) dict lookup
│   │   higher IC = more specific concept
│   │
│   └── output: CUIs with metadata + IC scores
│
├── STAGE 4: HIERARCHY REDUCTION
│   │
│   ├── ancestor_depth = log(20) / log(mean_in_degree), clamped [1, 5]
│   │   computed once from graph structure, not from query
│   │   SNOMED → 5 | ICD10 → 3 (fallback)
│   │
│   ├── rule: walk UP 1 hop per CUI
│   │   if parent ALSO in surviving set
│   │   AND IC(child) ≥ IC(parent)
│   │   AND same semantic type
│   │   → remove parent, keep child
│   │
│   └── output: reduced CUI set (parents removed)
│
├── STAGE 5: EMBEDDING REDUCTION
│   │
│   ├── size gate: _LOUVAIN_MIN_CUIS = 20
│   │   n ≤ 20 → fast path (Otsu + guards on full matrix)
│   │   n > 20 → full path (Louvain → Otsu + guards per community)
│   │
│   ├── FULL PATH (n > 20):
│   │   │
│   │   ├── k-NN graph
│   │   │   k_neighbors=20, _KNN_BLOCK_SIZE=2000
│   │   │   edge threshold = mean of 60 k-th neighbor distances (not all pairwise)
│   │   │
│   │   ├── Louvain community detection
│   │   │   resolution=1.0, _RANDOM_SEED=42
│   │   │   maximizes modularity (actual edges inside − expected by chance)
│   │   │   groups CUIs, removes nothing
│   │   │
│   │   └── within EACH community → Otsu + guards (below)
│   │
│   ├── OTSU THRESHOLD (per community or full matrix)
│   │   sort pairwise distances
│   │   try every split: score = w0 × w1 × (m0 − m1)²
│   │   highest score wins = natural gap between duplicates and different concepts
│   │   guardrail: cap at median (never > 50% of pairs below)
│   │   below threshold → check guards
│   │   above threshold → skip (definitely different)
│   │
│   ├── 4 STRUCTURAL GUARDS (pairs below threshold)
│   │   ANY fires → KEEP BOTH | ALL fail → remove lower IC
│   │   G1: hierarchy edge (O(1)) — parent-child → keep
│   │   G2: semantic types disjoint (O(|types|)) — Drug ≠ Disease → keep
│   │   G3: ancestor sets disjoint (BFS UP [1,5]) — different branches → keep
│   │   G4: sibling leaves (O(1)) — same parent, both leaves → keep
│   │
│   ├── singleton merging
│   │   merge_min_sim = mean(within-group) × 0.5, clamped [0.1, 0.9]
│   │   _COSINE_FALLBACK_THRESHOLD = 0.5
│   │
│   ├── confidence scoring (informational only — does NOT affect pipeline)
│   │   prox, cent, ret — variance-weighted, ranks output CSV only
│   │
│   └── output: deduplicated surviving CUIs
│
│
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  PIPELINE 2: TOPIC FORMATION                                       ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
│
├── STAGE 6: HIERARCHICAL TOPIC BUILDER
│   │
│   │ input: CUI codes only (no phrases, no text)
│   │
│   ├── adaptive parameters
│   │   IC floor = p10 of surviving CUI ICs (10th percentile, one number)
│   │   max_coverage = max(2, n/√n)
│   │
│   ├── BFS walk UP from every surviving CUI
│   │   max_depth = 5 (hard cap)
│   │   _HTB_IC_GRADIENT_RATIO = 0.3 (at hop 3+, stop if parent IC < 30% of current)
│   │   hop 1-2: always walk (grace period)
│   │   walk collects all ancestors → IC floor filters afterward
│   │
│   ├── 3 rules for grouping key (ALL must pass)
│   │   Rule 1: covers ≥ 2 surviving CUIs
│   │   Rule 2: IC ≥ floor
│   │   Rule 3: not in surviving set (must be an ancestor)
│   │
│   ├── convergence selection
│   │   sort passing ancestors by IC descending
│   │   greedy assign CUIs to highest-IC convergence points → subtopics
│   │   find ancestor of 2+ subtopics → topic grouper
│   │   unassigned CUIs → singletons
│   │
│   └── each topic gets:
│       label (SNOMED preferred term), topic_cui (matchable),
│       member CUIs, subtopics
│
├── STAGE 7: REPRESENTATIVES + ANCHORS
│   │
│   ├── per topic: group by semantic type → HAC (_REP_HAC_THRESHOLD=0.5)
│   │   → 1 rep per sub-cluster
│   │   selection: parent-within-set → embedding medoid → highest IC
│   │
│   └── anchors (documents only): BFS UP from reps
│       _ANCHOR_IC_MIN=4.0, _ANCHOR_BFS_DEPTH=4, _ANCHOR_IC_MAX_BROAD=3.0
│
├── STAGE 8: CENTROIDS
│   │
│   └── L2-normalized mean of member CUI embeddings (3072-dim)
│
│
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  PIPELINE 3: QUERY MATCHING                                        ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
│
├── ADAPTIVE PARAMETERS (computed once from store data)
│   │
│   ├── filter_min_ancestor_ic = p25(store CUI ICs)
│   ├── ic_weight_alpha = query_ic_mean / max_store_ic, clamped [0.1, 0.9]
│   ├── ic_prune_ratio = p10/p50(store ICs), clamped [0.1, 0.9]
│   ├── sibling_ic_ratio = p25/p75(store ICs), clamped [0.1, 0.95]
│   ├── use_idf = Shannon entropy of IDF > 0.3
│   └── min_best_lin = 2×root_ic / (q_ic+store_ic) × 1.5, clamped [0.03, 0.35]
│
├── PASS 1: TOPIC GATE
│   │
│   ├── step 1: centroid similarity (matrix multiply)
│   │   query centroid × all store centroids → gap_split (biggest gap)
│   │
│   ├── step 2: CUI overlap rescue
│   │   excluded topics with shared exact CUI → admitted
│   │
│   ├── step 3: fallback
│   │   zero admitted → score ALL topics in Pass 2
│   │
│   └── precompute: doc CUI ancestors (anc_depth=8), include topic_cui in matchable set
│
├── PASS 2: CUI SCORING (3 signals, no individual thresholds)
│   │
│   ├── signal 1: cui_ratio (IC-weighted CUI overlap)
│   │   per query CUI vs all topic CUIs, best match wins:
│   │     level 1: exact match → credit = 1.0
│   │     level 2: parent-child (8-hop BFS) → credit = IC(parent)/IC(child)
│   │     level 3: MICA sibling → credit = Lin(A,B)
│   │   cui_ratio = sum(credits) / n_query_CUIs
│   │
│   ├── signal 2: vec_sim (cosine similarity)
│   │   dot(query centroid, topic centroid)
│   │
│   ├── signal 3: lin_avg (hierarchy similarity)
│   │   for unmatched query CUIs: best Lin against all topic CUIs, averaged
│   │   Lin(A,B) = 2 × IC(MICA) / (IC(A) + IC(B))
│   │
│   └── output: 3 raw scores per candidate
│
├── PASS 3: Z-SCORE NORMALIZATION
│   │
│   ├── z = (value − mean) / std, per signal across all candidates
│   ├── final score = z_cui + z_vec + z_lin, shifted to [0, 1]
│   ├── highest-variance signal auto-dominates
│   └── flat fallback: w_cui=0.40, w_vec=0.30, w_lin=0.30
│
├── PASS 4: RELATIVE THRESHOLD
│   │
│   ├── threshold = best_score × score_ratio (score_ratio=0.40)
│   ├── score_min = 0.01 (structural floor)
│   ├── zero-evidence guard: suppress only if ALL 3 signals = 0.0
│   ├── no per-signal thresholds, no fixed result count cap
│   │
│   └── output: ranked results above threshold
│
└── LLM REASONING (optional)
    │
    └── top results → Gemini (LLM_MODEL, LLM_MAX_TOKENS=1500)
        matched CUIs + topic labels + chunk text → verdict
